{"id": 1469, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x沪江网校】作为一个过来人，你在学习新技能这件事上走过啥弯路？", "description": "别人上山走捷径，我走的简直就是弯成蚊香的盘山公路。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 6128, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170209105517OxMhDismIpwKnV2f.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-27T03:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 172288, "content": "哪有什么新技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816079}, {"id": 172289, "content": "每天醒来都想一次，今晚一定留点时间看书，结果回到家里累成狗状，玩玩手机又该睡觉了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841962}, {"id": 175105, "content": "两年前买的一本治拖延症的书，现在才想起来看。", "image": "img/option/option/20170306010334XBsd9cDiKAQaENP2.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959609}, {"id": 172290, "content": "各种鸡汤喝到吐，第二天早上还是起不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899903}, {"id": 175106, "content": "两年前买的一本治拖延症的书，现在才想起来看..", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 959609}, {"id": 175874, "content": "毅力不足的路都别想上，比如练字?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913404}, {"id": 175364, "content": "在沪江待了好多年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938518}, {"id": 172293, "content": "别人用1小时背的书我要用2小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951230}, {"id": 174088, "content": "用作业帮，学霸君一类的学习软件。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956261}, {"id": 172298, "content": "abacus", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 108900}, {"id": 186890, "content": "學一遍就過了，沒有內化成自己的知識體系", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475848}, {"id": 172299, "content": "花钱去上培训班，结果还是在培训课上玩手机玩的不亦乐乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951245}, {"id": 172300, "content": "看的听的学的那么多，但人际交流这个技能弯路要一走到黑了，是的我也许只是得了交流障碍症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733991}, {"id": 172301, "content": "18考研党，三小时考研专业，一小时本科专业（考资格证），一小时英语。因为梦想，所以坚持！最好远离电脑和手机等数码产品", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951253}, {"id": 175119, "content": "背单词永远只背到A打头的词", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686358}, {"id": 172304, "content": "只问成功者的经验，不问失败者的教训", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923647}, {"id": 174352, "content": "用百词斩背单词冲击英语考试，词没记得几个，图倒是影响深刻 。", "image": "img/option/option/201703041102133CVlsqhjkQeZTbtd", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802332}, {"id": 172305, "content": "购买课程不够谨慎，投入产出比太低", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949625}, {"id": 172306, "content": "有志者立长志 无智者常立志。立不少志。。都半途而废\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 579910}, {"id": 172309, "content": "四级427", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 943051}, {"id": 172310, "content": "看美剧可以练听力的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 244784}, {"id": 173078, "content": "花了钱了，随了大溜，该做的，不该做的都做了，就是没有走心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952888}, {"id": 172311, "content": "千萬不能上網校", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144054}, {"id": 172057, "content": "学习的时候不够专注", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651302}, {"id": 172313, "content": "模仿他人的学习方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951335}, {"id": 175385, "content": "以为看美剧能练英语，结果上去就看了破产姐妹，就学会了一个vagina", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 440582}, {"id": 172058, "content": "书本课程买买买，却没有往下学", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352556}, {"id": 172059, "content": "付费买的网课，一看到课程【永久有效】，就没学完过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 406, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2362}, {"id": 172315, "content": "对知识真正的认知度不够。从而从而把学习忽视了很久\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 944372}, {"id": 172060, "content": "背单词从来就没坚持下去过…", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 946271}, {"id": 172062, "content": "为了找靠谱的答案去了知乎 真正有用的答案没记住 能想起来的答案全是抖机灵", "image": null, "praise_count": 616, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325361}, {"id": 178462, "content": "热情只能维持下单到确认收货（╯' - ')╯︵ ┻━┻ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919839}, {"id": 172063, "content": "看韩剧并没有什么用。。。。注意力只在剧情上了。。。", "image": "img/option/option/20170227111525uPslBA2ZWKENdnRo.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889364}, {"id": 172065, "content": "abandon", "image": null, "praise_count": 917, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 172066, "content": "无数次减肥，无数次失败，最后学得一手无糖无盐的好菜?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818848}, {"id": 172067, "content": "健身后没有控制饮食，长膘速度比不健身的时候还要快", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147670}, {"id": 172323, "content": "下载一堆，最后又删", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950030}, {"id": 172068, "content": "学习一项新的东西时，觉得有趣，可过了一段时间，就觉得好枯燥", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 379240}, {"id": 180516, "content": "都忘记自己在APP上收藏过哪些东西了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738248}, {"id": 196388, "content": "每次拿起手机，只剩下娱乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004246}, {"id": 172069, "content": "坚持下去，坚持，下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869957}, {"id": 172070, "content": "以为念书好考试厉害就可以轻松地过这一生", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146002}, {"id": 183590, "content": "4.6级老师新东方永远第一页第一个单词", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981874}, {"id": 183591, "content": "4级考试准备一大堆教材，结合老友记，一直想着刷完后做题，考试时间到了，补考的心态去考，结果就过了→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981874}, {"id": 172072, "content": "为了日漫学日语，最后连日漫都不看了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 172328, "content": "mook的课程重来没有看完过……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917175}, {"id": 172074, "content": "每次出门拿好多书，结果一本也没看，就背着沉了……图书馆借书借一堆等到过期也没看几页……", "image": null, "praise_count": 378, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807778}, {"id": 172330, "content": "网课，用来攻克补考", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919744}, {"id": 172331, "content": "沪江网上做了的笔记都没回看过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818091}, {"id": 172076, "content": "为了X，买了一大堆Y，然后Y放成灰。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328264}]}